    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>As of 1.5 you can define a <code>package-info.java</code> file and provide a standard javadoc style comment for a package:</p>\n\n<p>com/foo/package-info.java:</p>\n\n<pre><code>/**\n * com.foo is a group of bar utils for operating on foo things.\n */\npackage com.foo;\n\n//rest of the file is empty\n</code></pre>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/specs/jls/se7/html/jls-7.html#jls-7.4.1\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Language specification for packages</a></p>\n"
  } ],
